tweet: #FeaturedConstituent Shannon Ortiz is no stranger to the struggles of mental health and suicide after losing her husband in 2016. Encouraged to see the phase 1 signing of a trade deal with #China. Important action on IP theft, trade secrets, and market access for American goods and services. Still work to be done, but I am thrilled to see this step in the right direction to force China to play by the rules.

I'll be doing another quarterly update tomorrow to talk about what my office accomplished in Q4 last year and answer some of your questions. Reply to this tweet with your question and I'll do my best to answer it!
